  "title": "Security Highlights from Ignite",
  "contentHtml": "In this episode Michael, Sarah, Gladys and Mark talk with guest Abbas Kudrati&nbsp;\n                  (\n                     <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/akudrati/?originalSubdomain=au/'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-linkedin\"></i></a>\n                  ) \n                  about some of the recent security news and announcements from the November 2021 Microsoft Ignite event. \n\n                  <br><br>\n\n                  <!-- Insert link from rss.com -->\n                  <iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://player.rss.com/azsecpodcast/319908?theme=light\" class=\"podcast-player\" title=\"rss embed thingy\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen><a href=\"https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/319908/\">MS Ignite Security Highlights | RSS.com Podcasting</a></iframe>\n\n                  <h5>Links</h5> \n                  <!-- Links to news articles -->\n                  <ul>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/319908/'>Transcript <i class=\"fa-solid fa-pencil\"></i></a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://news.microsoft.com/november-2021-ignite/\">Microsoft Ignite – November 2021</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://news.microsoft.com/ignite-november-2021-book-of-news/\">Microsoft Ignite Book of News</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/microsoft-defender-for-cloud/a-new-name-for-multi-cloud-security-microsoft-defender-for-cloud/ba-p/2943020\">A new name for multi-cloud security: Microsoft Defender for Cloud</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/microsoft-security-product-na